Safe data frame Modification

Source: R/utils_dataframe.R
rename_if_possible.Rd

Rename/remove a variable in a data frame if exists.

rename_if_possible(x, pattern, replacement)

remove_if_possible(x, pattern)

reorder_if_possible(x, cols)

Arguments

x

Data frame.
pattern

Variable to replace or remove.
replacement

New variable name.
cols

Order of columns.

Value

A modified data frame.

Examples

rename_if_possible(iris, "Sepal.Length", "length")
